headline: Randstad Named Leader and Star Performer in Everest Group PEAK Matrix® Assessment 2025 for US Contingent Talent and Strategic Solutions - Industrial
summary: Randstad has once again been recognized as a Leader in the Everest Group PEAK Matrix® Assessment 2025 for US Contingent Talent and Strategic Solutions – Industrial. This year, Randstad was also named a Star Performer, highlighting the company's year-over-year advancement in both market impact and delivery capability.
